closed_tickets_date_range.query: project in (BO,FI) AND type = "Service Request" and created >= "2024-08-07" and created <= "2024-12-31" AND status IN (Closed,"Resolved Non-Approval") AND "it-feol[select list (cascading)]" IS NOT EMPTY AND resolved >= {from_date} AND resolved <= {to_date} ORDER BY created DESC

in_progress_tickets.query: project in (BO,FI) AND type = "Service Request" and created >= "2024-08-07" and created <= "2024-12-31" AND status IN ("Escalated Non-Approval", "Technical In Progress Non-Approval", "Technical Awaiting Vendor", "Awaiting End User Response", "Awaiting End User Response Non-Approval", "Technical Awaiting Vendor Non-Approval") AND "it-feol[select list (cascading)]" IS NOT EMPTY ORDER BY created DESC
